data.description: Location!!! Lowest priced home in the highly desired neighborhood of Sabal Harbour with an abundance of amenities: tennis/pickleball courts, pool, playground, basketball court, and clubhouse all for a low monthly HOA fee of $69!!  Put your personal touches on this 3/2 home! If you're looking for an investment property, this community has no rental restrictions. NEW ROOF IN 2020! The primary bedroom has a walk-in closet and en-suite bathroom. This home boasts a Split bedroom plan, a large great room, vaulted ceilings, and a covered back patio. One mile to PUBLIX, banks, restaurants, and more!
